Title: Community Climb
Description:
For youth or adults new to climbing
- YMCA staff and volunteers will belay and give basic instructions for harnessing and climbing techniques and terms.
- No belay instruction or certification during community climb.
- Harnesses and shoes are provided.
- Parents who are YMCA belay certified may belay their own children.
